    <h2>Neural Gateways Lab</h2>
    <p>The Neural Gateways Lab investigates how forebrain circuits manage the flow and processing of sensory information.
Focusing on circuits in thalamus and cortex, we use in-house and open-access datasets to elucidate their connectivity and functional interactions.
